text: haey a l laoh ban bangkeut satv del meanchivit teangoasa ampi tuk . haey knongchamnaom puokvea mean satv del vea r nung poh robsa vea haey muoychamnuon tiet mean satv del daer cheung pir haey muoychamnuon tiet mean satv del daer cheung buon . a l laoh nung bangkeut nouv avei del trong mean chetnea . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh mean anoupheap leu avei teangoasa
